{"tid":1369279,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"東華三院不代表我《社會服務科員工聯合聲明》","createTime":"2019-07-26T16:08:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-27T04:20:54.000Z","uid":291031,"like":61,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"cff47532b95b9be2c3cb5941982c64ebc35ed368","tid":1369279,"uid":291031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T16:08:36.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">東華聲明不代表我！！</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">我們是社工，不是維穩工具！</span></div><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n致香港政府及全體香港市民：<br />\n我們是一班熱愛香港的東華三院社會服務科員工。此時此刻，我們正面臨重大的道德危機，委身於社會服務的我們絕對有責任去喚醒公眾人士的關注，而不是作維穩機器。<br />\n<br />\n(一)在全球<br />\n國際社會工作者聯會(IFSW)和國際社會工作教育聯盟(IASSW) 一直都共同制定社會工作全球定義。它們同時指出社工的本質是<span style=\"color: red;\">守護人權與社會公義</span>。<br />\n<br />\n(二) 在香港<br />\n按香港社工註冊局工作守則 (49條)，<strong><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">當政府</span></strong></strong>、社團或機構的政策、程序或活動導致或構成任何人士陷入困境及痛苦，又或是妨礙困境及痛苦的解除時，社工認同有需要喚起決策者或公眾人士對這些情況的關注。<br />\n<br />\n(三) 在東華三院<br />\n東華三院貴為全港歷史最悠久及規模最大的慈善服務機構，我們定將繼續堅守和發揚東華三院的慈善精神，致力為市民大眾構建更美好的社會及服務。<br />\n<br />\n因而我們發出呼喊，懇請每一位都能夠運用自己的聲音和方法，向政府施壓，<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>將不公平的政權中止！</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n在此，重新宣讀新七大訴求：<br />\n1. 撤回逃犯條例<br />\n2. 撤回612暴動定義<br />\n3. 釋放被捕人士、撤回所有抗爭者控罪<br />\n4. 成立獨立調查委員會、並追究警隊濫權<br />\n5. 承諾不在港推行社會信用評分制<br />\n6. 追究元朗警黑勾結<br />\n7. 立即實行雙普選<br />\n<br />\n我們會繼續緊守崗位，為市民服務，一個也不能少。<br />\n<br />\n註：東華三院社會服務科員工數目眾多，本聲明只代表已對本聲明表示同意的同事。<br />\n<br />\n一班熱愛香港的東華三院社會服務科員工 敬上<br />\n二零一九年七月二十六日<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Xrg9MLh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXrg9MLh.jpg&h=c4459faf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1muO2iC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1muO2iC.jpg&h=e8351003&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9E4WrLh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9E4WrLh.jpg&h=7f22f6f0&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uSZCVDC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuSZCVDC.jpg&h=86b29ec6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kSKvwbY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkSKvwbY.jpg&h=59140fc3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7a8ae54f0028dafcdeafb2232b40608b0d07bbea","tid":1369279,"uid":291031,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T16:13:47.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b1b34dc2871155fbcee2cd1a5f96664ab7b54b89","tid":1369279,"uid":265733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T16:15:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86cb6ff0f9a543b81a867b0e8166e13bdb9b295b","tid":1369279,"uid":291031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T16:16:41.000Z","msg":"我無野講"},{"pid":"c0c76c97dcfb4222be08c07a6c556099dbdf3604","tid":1369279,"uid":129309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T16:20:54.000Z","msg":"多謝"},{"pid":"c3bfd33e60dd79225ab929fb80819734843ee238","tid":1369279,"uid":291031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T16:22:04.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6755fb3e71079e542c12432f44ff88ee8d2d21b0","tid":1369279,"uid":291031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T16:26:54.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5ebd981cdcfe90be4fbe2e05faa7f5bba019bc25","tid":1369279,"uid":291031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T16:28:24.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4b6b544e1a50f02a2ec484e7f03c297ac84f8eaf","tid":1369279,"uid":291031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T16:35:29.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f4d277416b9f9be5ba2f3638c67e0c6c0a35fc14","tid":13